data.title: Alumni/Faculty/Staff Vertical Files
data.meta_description: Browse the Inman E. Page Library files for alumni, faculty and staff.
data.text:
The Alumni/Faculty/Staff Vertical Files are a compilation of files containing information about an individual that either attended or was employed by Lincoln Univeristy of Missouri. Files may contain documents, letters, obituaries, newspaper articles, published and unpublished writings or photographs. The information collected is filed under the individual's name, last name first. For married women, please check for both their married and maiden names. For a listing of files on University Presidents (Principals) and Administrators (Board of Curators), please see Presidential Vertical Files and Board of Curators Vertical Files.

The various files contain the information we have available on an individual and do not include information that may be contained in other collections, such as the Faye Tull Carter Collection, that are housed in the University Archvies/Ethnic Studies Center.
